BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Apex Intelligence: Leveraging AI for Small Business
DTSTART;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260326T080000
DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260326T090000
UID:0d48c80c9efecc5e2cf354c0a0cf2523@growthzone.com
DESCRIPTION:AI isn't the future\, it's happening now! Small businesses hav
 e a unique advantage: we're agile\, we understand our customers deeply\, a
 nd we can implement and iterate without corporate red tape. But tools alon
 e aren't enough. Success requires knowing which AI solutions actually solv
 e your problems\, how to use them strategically\, and how to stay human in
  an increasingly automated world. Whether you're running a solo venture\, 
 managing a growing team\, or navigating the rapidly changing landscape of 
 small business\, come join this community of forward-thinking owners ready
  to harness AI strategically. Together\, we'll share practical AI tools an
 d strategies\, learn from each other's experiments and successes\, and bui
 ld a supportive network that helps us all stay competitive in an AI-driven
  economy. Springhill Suites Apex 1100 Marco Drive Apex\, NC 27502
LOCATION:Apex\, NC
URL:https://business.apexchamber.com/events/details/apex-intelligence-leve
 raging-ai-for-small-business
X-SOURCE:Apex Chamber of Commerce
END:VEVENT
